This folder contains all modifications needed to add libvpx support to xuggle-fmpeg using its captive compiling system.

Contents:

- Makefile.am -> Automake file with newly added variable names
- configure.ac -> Added libvpx support
- libvpx\ -> Folder containing libvpx 0.96 using xuggle incarceration system

Instructions:

- execute "git submodule init" & "git submodule update" to grab latest libvpx libraries.
- To apply it to xuggle-ffmpeg just overwrite root folder with all the archives provided.
- Execute 'autoreconf' on xuggle-ffmepg root folder to update all generated config files.
- Then it should compile cleanly

Enjoy!


 
